---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Trade & Fair Use Policy | YourHQ"
  description="No lock-ins. No surprises. No holding your site hostage. You own your domain, your content, and your design from day one."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="bg-bone min-h-screen font-sans text-carbon selection:bg-deepGreen selection:text-white pb-24">

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-16 px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mb-6">Terms of Trade &amp; Fair Use Policy</p>
        
        <h1 class="font-display text-display font-bold text-carbon mb-8">
          The Plain English Version.
        </h1>
        
        <!-- The Whisper / Tension Technique -->
        <p class="font-serif italic text-headline text-terracotta leading-snug mb-6">
          No lock-ins. No surprises. No holding your site hostage.
        </p>
        <p class="font-sans text-subhead text-softGrey leading-relaxed">
          You own your domain, your content, and your design from day one.<br/>
          If you ever leave, I hand everything over.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE DOCUMENT -->
    <article class="px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-elegant border border-carbon/5 p-8 md:p-16 lg:p-20">
        
        <div class="space-y-16">

          <!-- 01 PAYMENTS -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">01</span> Payments
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p>Setup fees are paid 100% upfront to secure your build slot. I allocate dedicated time to your project immediately on booking.</p>
              <p>Monthly Caretaker fees are billed automatically from your go-live date. Month-to-month. No fixed term. Cancel anytime with 30 days notice.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 02 GUARANTEE -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">02</span> The Guarantee. Love It or Leave It.
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p>I build your complete site before you commit to the subscription. You receive a private preview link. The finished site, not a mockup.</p>
              
              <ul class="space-y-3 border-l-2 border-carbon/10 pl-6 my-6">
                <li><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Love it.</strong> Domain connects, site goes live, subscription starts.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Don't love it.</strong> Full refund of your setup fee, minus:</li>
              </ul>
              
              <ul class="space-y-2 pl-12 list-disc list-outside marker:text-carbon/20">
                <li>Stripe processing fees (~3%)</li>
                <li>Domain registration costs if already purchased</li>
              </ul>
              
              <p class="pt-2">The refund is available before the site goes live. Once live and the subscription has started, the setup fee is non-refundable.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 03 ON-DEMAND UPDATES -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">03</span> What's Included in On-Demand Updates
            </h2>
            <div class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p class="mb-8">All Caretaker subscriptions include on-demand updates. Just text or email. I handle it.</p>
              
              <p class="font-mono text-badge text-deepGreen mb-4">Included</p>
              <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-deepGreen mr-3 mt-1">✓</span> Text changes. Phone numbers, hours, pricing, service descriptions.</li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-deepGreen mr-3 mt-1">✓</span> Photo swaps. New photos, gallery updates, team photos.</li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-deepGreen mr-3 mt-1">✓</span> Content edits. Updating existing copy to keep things current.</li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-deepGreen mr-3 mt-1">✓</span> Contact detail changes.</li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-deepGreen mr-3 mt-1">✓</span> Minor content additions within existing page structure.</li>
              </ul>
              
              <p class="font-mono text-badge text-terracotta mb-4">Quoted Separately</p>
              <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-terracotta mr-3 mt-1">✕</span> New pages beyond your original site structure.</li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-terracotta mr-3 mt-1">✕</span> New third-party integrations.</li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-terracotta mr-3 mt-1">✕</span> Major restructures or new features.</li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-terracotta mr-3 mt-1">✕</span> Blog post writing or content creation.</li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-terracotta mr-3 mt-1">✕</span> Design changes beyond routine content updates (see the Design Refresh Add-On).</li>
              </ul>

              <p class="font-mono text-badge text-carbon mb-4">The 30-minute rule</p>
              <p class="mb-8">Any single request that looks like it will take more than 30 minutes of dev work will be given a written estimate before anything starts. You decide whether to proceed. No surprises. Applies equally to every tier.</p>

              <p class="font-serif italic text-accent text-carbon border-l-2 border-carbon/10 pl-6">
                If you're not sure whether something's included, just ask. I'll always tell you before any costs apply.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 04 RESPONSE TIMES -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">04</span> Response Times
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p>Same response window for every Caretaker tier. Tiers reflect how active your site is, not who gets answered first.</p>
              <ul class="space-y-3 border-l-2 border-carbon/10 pl-6 my-4">
                <li><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">First response.</strong> Within one business day.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Standard updates.</strong> Shipped within two to three business days of your approval.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Urgent fixes.</strong> Site down, payment flow broken, security issue. Same business day, regardless of tier.</li>
              </ul>
              <p>Business hours: Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm NZST, excluding New Zealand public holidays. Requests outside business hours are picked up the next business day.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 05 ANNUAL REFRESH -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">05</span> Annual Design Refresh
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p>Included in every Caretaker subscription. On or around your 12-month anniversary, I refresh your site's visual design. Layout, typography, hero section, colour updates. To keep it current.</p>
              <p>The refresh is a design update to existing content. It does not include new pages, new integrations, or expanded scope. These are quoted separately.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 06 ADDITIONAL WORK -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">06</span> Additional Work
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-6 font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p>Any work outside your included updates is available at <strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">$175/hr NZD + GST</strong>.</p>
              
              <div>
                <p class="font-mono text-badge text-carbon mb-4">How it works</p>
                <ol class="space-y-3 list-decimal list-outside pl-5 marker:font-mono marker:text-signal marker:text-sm">
                  <li class="pl-2">You request it. Text or email with what you need.</li>
                  <li class="pl-2">I provide a written estimate. Hours and total cost. Before starting.</li>
                  <li class="pl-2">You approve it. I don't start until you say go.</li>
                  <li class="pl-2">I complete and invoice. Billed on your next monthly cycle.</li>
                </ol>
              </div>
              
              <p class="font-semibold text-carbon bg-surface p-4 rounded-lg border border-carbon/5 inline-block">
                No surprises. No bill shock. You're always in control.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 07 CANCELLATION -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">07</span> Cancellation
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p>30 days written notice. Text or email is fine.</p>
              <p>Your site stays live during the notice period. On cancellation I provide a full static export of your site files. Your domain remains yours, registered in your name from day one.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 08 PAUSING -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">08</span> Pausing
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p>You can pause your subscription for up to three months. Your site stays live, hosting continues, and security stays tight. No penalty.</p>
              <p>After three months, we'll be in touch to work out what happens from there. No penalty. Resume whenever you're ready within the pause window.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 09 OWNERSHIP -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">09</span> Ownership
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">You own your domain.</strong> Registered in your name, not mine.</p>
              <p><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">You own your content.</strong> All text, images, and files you provide.</p>
              <p><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">You own your design.</strong> Created for you, not licensed to you.</p>
              <p><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">You own your customer data.</strong> I do not mine, sell, or share it.</p>
              <p class="font-serif italic text-carbon/70 pt-2">I claim no intellectual property rights over anything on your site.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 10 LIABILITY -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">10</span> Liability
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p>I aim for high uptime and reliable performance.</p>
              <p>YourHQ is not liable for loss of business due to outages outside our control. Including hosting network issues, third-party platform outages, or force majeure events.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 11 CONTENT QUALITY -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">11</span> Content Quality
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p>I work with what's actually there. If your existing photos or content aren't up to standard, I'll tell you honestly before we build. Not after.</p>
              <p>I won't use low-quality material just to fill space. If we need to source alternatives, I'll flag it and we'll work it out before anything goes live.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- 12 GOVERNING LAW -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-subhead text-carbon mb-6 flex items-baseline">
              <span class="font-mono text-badge text-signal mr-4">12</span> Governing Law
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:pl-9">
              <p>These terms are governed by the laws of New Zealand. Any disputes will be resolved under New Zealand jurisdiction.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

        </div>

        <!-- FOOTER / SIGN OFF -->
        <section class="border-t border-carbon/10 mt-20 pt-10 font-mono text-badge text-softGrey md:pl-9">
          <p class="mb-4">Last updated: May 2026</p>
          <p class="mb-1 text-carbon">YourHQ Limited</p>
          <p class="mb-1"><a href="mailto:hello@yourhq.co.nz" class="hover:text-signal transition-colors">hello@yourhq.co.nz</a> &middot; <a href="sms:0221725793" class="hover:text-signal transition-colors">022 172 5793</a></p>
          <p>Whangārei, Aotearoa New Zealand</p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </article>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>